item.title: CVE-2017-20121|2024-08-05T21:45:25.993Z -- teradici -- management%20console
item.description: A vulnerability was found in Teradici Management Console 2.2.0. It has been declared as critical. Affected by this vulnerability is an unknown functionality of the component Database Management. The manipulation leads to improper privilege management. It is possible to launch the attack on the local host. The exploit has been disclosed to the public and may be used.
